init_original_verilog_files(25.10)          init_original_verilog_files(25.10)

Name
       init_original_verilog_files

Syntax
       init_original_verilog_files name

       Type: String

       Specifies  a  list  of  Verilog files to be read during initialization.
       init_design will set it to the list of input files  given  to  it.  The
       original  input file names are retained through the flow for reference,
       and used by write_do_lec for the default golden netlist comparison file
       names.

Related Information
              * init_design

              * write_do_lec

